title: A Review of 1226 Mike Baker
description:
Mike is a former CIA agent and has a great deal of information about how our intelligence agency works. He has great insight into how our government works and spends our money. This conversation is another great one that will teach you a lot while making you laugh. Mike has a new show coming out that will go into the spending of the CIA called Black Files. Check it out!

Enjoy my review folks!
